title: Sinister_Entity-Sinister_Entity-2002-VTU
description:
I thought I should blow some dust of this old mini-cd because this year
(2013) we did reband to work on a new 4 track ep.

And a little info on us:

J.K. - Vocals. (ex. Godseye)
K.N. - Guitars. (S.I.X.)
J.F. - Bass. (Magenta Harvest, The Iniquity Descent, Under Jord)
J.F. - Drums. (In Divinia, ex. Social Sterility, Tinnitus)

We ain't proud of this shit, but we had fun making it.
Feel free to comment!!
